Code-Class  |  React, CSS, Javascript, Firebase, Firestore, Authentication, Cloud Function
Demo Link: https://capstone-ide.web.app/
    • Designed and developed a coding website that facilitates real-time collaboration in a classroom environment for multiple users.
    • Implemented an IDE consisting of an Ace editor integrated with Firebase for seamless real-time code editing and synchronization.
    • Incorporated a compiler feature that leverages a cloud function to communicate with an external Jdoodle API service, enabling code execution in 14 programming languages.
    • Implemented a user display feature that shows all users currently present in the classroom, promoting a sense of community and interaction.
    • Utilized Firebase authentication for secure user sign-in and room tracking.
